title: Ep 22: Know Thyself with Melissa Villasenor
description: Mellisa Villasenor and I discuss self and how to find it. Also, why it's AWFUL to compare yourself to others. Melissa is an amazing impressionist and comic and I know you'll adore her as I do.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
